OL,3,CAngela Rayner: No commitment to lift
OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap by next election
OL,6,FAngela Rayner dodged questions about
OL,7,Fwhether the two-child limit would be
OL,8,Faxed.
OL,10,FThe two-child limit was introduced
OL,11,Funder the Conservative Government in
OL,12,F2017, and restricts Child Tax Credit
OL,13,Fand Universal Credit to the first two
OL,14,Fchildren in most households.
OL,16,FIn May, Labour leader Sir Keir Starmer
OL,17,Fsaid he would scrap the cap "in an
OL,18,Fideal world" but added that "we
OL,19,Fhaven't got the resources to do it at
OL,20,Fthe moment".
