OL,3,CAngela Rayner: No commitment to lift
OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap by next election
OL,6,FA report from the End Child Poverty
OL,7,FCoalition earlier this month found
OL,8,Fchild poverty rates are directly and
OL,9,Fstrongly correlated with the
OL,10,Fpercentage of children affected by the
OL,11,Ftwo-child limit in the local area.
OL,13,FIt argued that this provides "further
OL,14,Fevidence that the policy is a key
OL,15,Fdriver of child poverty".
OL,17,FRayner also faced questions on her
OL,18,Fdecision to continue to serve under
OL,19,FJeremy Corbyn's leadership of the
OL,20,FLabour party.
