OL,3,CAngela Rayner: No commitment to lift
OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap by next election
OL,6,F"For me, I felt it was my obligation
OL,7,Fto do my utmost to be an opposition
OL,8,Fwhen my constituents was feeling the
OL,9,Ffull brunt of the conservatives," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"And therefore the question was never
OL,13,Fabout who our leader was. The question
OL,14,Ffor me was fighting for that change
OL,15,Fthat I so desperately want to see."
OL,17,FShadow Chancellor Rachel Reeves was
OL,18,Falso questioned by Anushka Asthana,
OL,19,Fduring the interview in a pub in
OL,20,FCannock, Staffordshire.
