OL,6,FResponding to Corbyn's recent claim
OL,7,Fthat he would win if he led Labour
OL,8,Finto this election, she laughed: "Well
OL,9,Fhe lot two elections didn't he? He had
OL,10,Fhis chance."
OL,12,FWhen the conversation moved to
OL,13,Fchildhood political heroes, the two
OL,14,Fwomen tipped to become the two most
OL,15,Fpowerful in the country had varied
OL,16,Fresponses.
